Unfortunately, not many discord servers are using such bots. So tc!

Just learned about a new crypto scam from DefiLlama:

Scam through genuine crypto weblinks on Google Ads.

Here's how:

An ad for a genuine crypto website is put on Google with their actual URL.
But when someone clicks on it, they are redirected to a scam website through an ad network kochava.com

Recommended precaution:

Never click any Google ad or sponsored links. Always go with the organic search results. Better still confirm the links from trusted sources like CoinGecko, CMC, DefiLlama etc.
